Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.98,0:00:13.82,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:9989,13826}I can feel the sunshine on me,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.82,0:00:17.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:13826,17121}I think I'll bask in it a little more.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.12,0:00:22.12,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:18122,22126}It's a beginning of a new day.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.33,0:00:28.46,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:25338,28466}That's the moment I like the most,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.34,0:00:33.51,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:29342,33513}the one that starts it all.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.51,0:00:36.84,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:33513,36849}Something lovely is about to happen,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.84,0:00:40.72,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:36849,40728}I just have a hunch like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.72,0:00:48.40,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:40728,48403}Woom! My reflection the mirror
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.40,0:00:52.28,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:48403,52282}Woom! Looks rather pretty.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.28,0:00:56.03,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:52282,56035}It feels so nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.03,0:01:02.87,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:56035,62875}I reach out to the clear blue sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.79,0:01:10.67,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:63793,70675}I'm so excited and filled with hope.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.46,0:01:15.09,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:71467,75096}Love, work, everything,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.09,0:01:18.60,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:75096,78600}I want to take these challenges on
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.60,0:01:24.89,saint tail op en,[karaoke],0,0,0,,{TIME:78600,84897}and build myself again.
Comment: 0,0:01:35.11,0:01:35.11,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:95116,95116}Part A
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.30,0:01:57.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:112300,117263}Excuse me, aren't you Emi Honma,\Nthe teenage idol?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.13,0:02:00.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:118139,120475}Yes. Have we met somewhere?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.68,0:02:04.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:120683,124312}– I see your picture in the magazines.\N– I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.56,0:02:07.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:124562,127732}What brings you here today?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.06,0:02:13.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:129067,133237}You don't have to say if it puts\Nsomeone in a difficult situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.78,0:02:17.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:133780,137784}No, I want to tell you.\NThe truth is, I have a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.03,0:02:22.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:138034,142622}I've been dating someone, but no one,\Nnot even my management agency, knows.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.87,0:02:25.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:142872,145291}I put a picture\Ntaken of us together…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.54,0:02:28.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:145541,148836}…in my locket\Nand always kept it near me.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.08,0:02:32.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:149087,152507}Once, when I left it in\Nmy dressing room for a moment…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.75,0:02:37.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:152757,157095}…Mr. Iwasaki from a rival\Nproduction came and stole it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.42,0:02:38.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:157428,158596}Oh, dear.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.34,0:02:43.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:159347,163810}And then Mr. Iwasaki came\Nto me and said:
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.89,0:02:49.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:164894,169774}Let me see, what should I do\Nabout this, this picture?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.23,0:02:54.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:171234,174320}The press would go crazy\Nif I sold it to them.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.57,0:02:57.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:174570,177240}But that would mean\Nthe end of your career.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:57.49,0:03:01.74,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:177490,181744}– Please, give it back to me!\N– OK, I'll give it back to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.99,0:03:05.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:181994,185164}In exchange, your part\Nas Yoko in that new movie…
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.41,0:03:09.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:185415,189377}…you could turn down the part\Nand give it to one of my girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.33,0:03:13.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:190336,193047}You could pretend to be sick\Nor something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:13.29,0:03:18.09,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:193297,198094}If you don't do it, I won't be\Nresponsible for this picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:19.80,0:03:21.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:199804,201013}How terrible!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.26,0:03:23.72,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:201264,203725}I don't want to cause trouble\Nfor my agency.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.97,0:03:26.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:203975,206894}I came here because\NI don't know what to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.14,0:03:31.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:207145,211816}Please cheer up.\NI'm sure God will help you.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.10,0:03:37.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:213109,217822}SAVE THE PRETTY IDOL GIRL!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:41.11,0:03:42.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:221117,222827}Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.32,0:03:46.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:224328,226581}Big news, big news!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.78,0:03:47.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:226789,227832}Sawatari.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.91,0:03:51.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:228916,231586}The shampoo company's\Nimage girl contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.83,0:03:54.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:231836,234839}Look, you passed\Nthe preliminaries! See?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.50,0:03:59.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:236507,239260}Wow! That's great!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.47,0:04:05.76,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:241471,245767}Yep, you're one step closer\Nto becoming a big star.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.97,0:04:09.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:245975,249645}– This is great!\N– You'll go to the contest, won't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.89,0:04:11.39,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:249896,251397}Just hold on there!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.64,0:04:15.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:251647,255610}And when you become a big star,\Ndon't forget about us!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.86,0:04:16.98,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:255860,256986}Listen…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.23,0:04:22.40,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:257236,262408}No way! She'll be so busy, she won't\Neven be able to come to school!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.65,0:04:24.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:262658,264911}– Oh, wow!\N– Sawatari!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.91,0:04:30.50,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:265912,270500}If you think becoming a big star\Nis that easy, you're crazy!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.12,0:04:38.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:274128,278591}– What's with him? Spoilsport.\N– Really.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.21,0:04:42.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:279217,282053}I wonder, was it something we said?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.30,0:04:45.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:282303,285556}I don't think so, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.97,0:04:49.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:285973,289268}Oh, I almost forgot.\NRina also passed. See?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.51,0:04:51.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:289519,291771}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.31,0:04:56.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:294315,296734}I'm pretty sure she entered herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.98,0:04:59.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:296984,299320}She has a lot\Nof confidence in herself.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.99,0:05:08.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:303991,308412}I'm not going to participate\Nin the contest! No way!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.66,0:05:13.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:308663,313417}Now, Meimi, listen. That girl Emi\Nwho came here yesterday for help…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:16.33,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:313668,316337}The one who wants her locket?\NI'll do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.58,0:05:22.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:316587,322009}You don't understand. Emi is one\Nof the judges for that contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.21,0:05:24.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:322218,324804}She was one of the past winners.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.22,0:05:28.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:325221,328599}And that Mr. Iwasaki is\Nalso one of the judges.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.85,0:05:32.85,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:328850,332854}Unless Emi announces she is turning\Ndown the role by that day…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.10,0:05:36.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:333104,336816}…he says he'll publicize the picture\Nafter the contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.06,0:05:40.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:337066,340820}I think our best bet would be\Nto get the locket…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.02,0:05:44.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:341028,344198}…during the contest\Nand return it to Emi.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.65,0:05:47.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:344657,347660}But why do I have to enter a contest?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.74,0:05:51.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:349745,351622}I understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.87,0:05:56.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:351873,356210}I would never have guessed that\Nyou were so afraid of contests.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.46,0:06:01.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:356460,361340}– Just hold on there!\N– Forget it. Just forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.59,0:06:07.22,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:361591,367221}Who says I'm afraid? All right then,\NI'll show you. I'll enter that contest!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.84,0:06:09.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:367847,369307}Forgive me, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.77,0:06:21.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:376772,381193}I didn't mean to say what I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.03,0:06:29.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:388034,389243}A note!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.70,0:06:35.12,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:391704,395124}"On the day of the beauty contest,\NI'll take a locket…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.37,0:06:40.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:395374,400254}…from Mr. Iwasaki of the Rainbow\NProduction Company. – St. Tail"
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.42,0:06:44.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:402423,404425}Hey, come back here!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:53.64,0:06:56.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:413643,416687}Rina. Give it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.93,0:06:59.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:416938,419774}Did you hear?\NI'm entering that contest too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.02,0:07:02.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:420024,422193}I want to test my capabilities.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.61,0:07:05.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:422610,425947}The one Sawatari was talking about,\Nyou're in it too?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:08.15,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:426197,428157}Will you come and watch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.69,0:07:12.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:428699,432161}Why do I have to go?\NGirls are a pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.41,0:07:15.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:432411,435373}Oh, all right. Now give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.62,0:07:20.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:435623,440628}That's all you think about, St. Tail!\NIt was a man dressed like a girl!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.13,0:07:27.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:443130,447551}There's a future star\Nstanding right in front of you!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.47,0:07:31.55,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:449470,451555}Give it back!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.72,0:07:39.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:455726,459563}Asuka Jr., have you, you know,\Ngotten taller?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.81,0:07:45.69,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:459814,465695}I'd better make my move. Soon the\Nother girls will start noticing him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.36,0:07:51.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:468364,471867}I'd better stake my claim on him.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:00.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:478499,480793}I'm home!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.21,0:08:03.62,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:481210,483629}– Hi there!\N– Hi, Meimi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.87,0:08:08.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:483879,488259}– Emi Honma's being interviewed on TV.\N– Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.71,0:08:11.67,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:488718,491679}Emi, congratulations\Non getting the role of Yoko.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.92,0:08:16.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:491929,496600}Thank you.\NI owe everything to all my fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.80,0:08:21.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:496809,501731}And does that include your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.98,0:08:25.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:501981,505735}My boyfriend is all of my fans.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.52,0:08:28.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:506527,508738}Poor Emi, it must be hard for her.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.61,0:08:32.95,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:509613,512950}She's right. She's too young\Nto have a boyfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:33.15,0:08:34.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:513159,514910}I wouldn't be so sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.11,0:08:39.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:515119,519457}Even junior high kids have\Nsignificant others these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.66,0:08:45.04,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:519665,525046}Meimi, you don't have a boyfriend,\Ndo you? You're much too young.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.42,0:08:51.01,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:527423,531010}I never imagined!\NMy Meimi's got a boyfriend!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.26,0:08:52.21,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:531260,532219}I what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.47,0:08:55.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:532470,535347}Oh, dear, my idyllic life\Nis coming to an end.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.59,0:09:00.56,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:535598,540561}Calm down, dear. Meimi hasn't said\Nanything about liking a certain boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.81,0:09:03.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:540811,543230}What? You don't like boys?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.48,0:09:06.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:543481,546609}Does that mean you prefer girls?\NThat is a problem.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.85,0:09:08.94,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:546859,548944}Let's have a heart-to-heart talk.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.19,0:09:11.36,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:549195,551363}I'm going to my room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.61,0:09:14.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:551614,554075}– Enough of this nonsense!\N– But, Eimi…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.16,0:09:24.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:561165,564460}I'm home, Ruby. Did you miss me?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.04,0:09:28.63,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:565044,568631}You're my best friend, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:35.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:573552,575971}Sorry. I had something on my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.01,0:09:44.48,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:579016,584480}If I become a star,\NI wonder if he'll look at me.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.40,0:09:54.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:592404,594573}We've been waiting for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.82,0:09:58.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:594824,598077}My name is Yamashiro.\NI'm in charge of this contest.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.28,0:10:01.16,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:598285,601163}This is Mr. Iwasaki\Nfrom Rainbow Productions.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.41,0:10:02.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:601413,602373}Hello.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.62,0:10:06.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:602623,606418}You'd better arrest that burglar.\NShe's such a nuisance!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.83,0:10:08.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:606836,608420}I'm doing my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.88,0:10:13.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:609880,613884}Your father may be a detective,\Nbut how will you arrest her?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.13,0:10:18.97,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:614135,618973}Judging from this building's floor\Nplan and her mode of operation…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.22,0:10:23.81,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:619223,623811}…there's a high possibility\Nshe'll appear directly on-stage.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.06,0:10:28.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:624061,628149}And so I thought we could rig\Nthe stage curtain…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.39,0:10:32.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:628399,632319}…to fall on her like a casting net,\Nthus trapping her.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.82,0:10:35.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:632820,635281}I understand. You have my permission.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.53,0:10:39.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:635531,639493}I will capture her.\NI won't fail this time.
Comment: 0,0:10:42.99,0:10:42.99,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:642997,642997}Eyecatch
Comment: 0,0:10:48.00,0:10:48.00,[chapter],[chapter],0,0,0,,{TIME:648002,648002}Part B
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.29,0:10:54.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:652298,654758}And now the contest begins.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.21,0:10:58.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:655217,658804}First is a question-and-answer\Nsegment, then a camera test.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.05,0:11:01.68,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:659054,661682}Entry 1, please come forward!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.10,0:11:05.47,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:663100,665477}Entry 1, Manami Yoshizawa.\NI'm 16 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.72,0:11:08.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:665728,668189}What are you currently most devoted to?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.43,0:11:10.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:668439,670274}To my music and dancing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.48,0:11:14.52,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:670482,674528}I am also serious about putting\Nevery effort into this audition.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.77,0:11:15.73,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:674778,675738}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.98,0:11:19.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:675988,679450}– What are your dreams for the future?\N– To become an actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.03,0:11:22.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:680034,682453}– Please turn to the right.\N– Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:22.70,0:11:26.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:682703,686415}All right. Now turn around and smile.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.66,0:11:30.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:686665,690586}Make a complete turn.\NThat's fine, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.83,0:11:34.88,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:690836,694882}– This isn't easy, is it?\N– Next contestant, entry 2.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.21,0:11:38.96,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:696217,698969}My name is Mutsumi Hijiri.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.01,0:11:42.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:700012,702348}My name is Yoko Hizawa.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.09,0:11:45.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:703098,705100}My name is Yuki Uchida.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.35,0:11:49.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:705351,709355}Seira, where's Rina and Meimi?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.93,0:11:53.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:709939,713067}– I'm sure they'll be out soon.\N– I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.31,0:11:56.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:713317,716904}My name is Rina Takamiya.\NI'm 14 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.15,0:11:59.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:717154,719573}I'm pleased to meet you all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.07,0:12:03.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:720074,723077}15, is there someone special\Nin your life now?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.99,0:12:06.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:724995,726580}Yes, there is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.79,0:12:16.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:732795,736590}All right, smile.\NNow turn to the right.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.84,0:12:22.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:736840,742388}Darn that St. Tail. Why does she\Nwant the locket Mr. Iwasaki has?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.63,0:12:24.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:742638,744640}I don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.51,0:12:30.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:745516,750187}Never mind. I've got to concentrate\Non capturing her, that's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.39,0:12:32.43,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:750396,752439}All right, come on, St. Tail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.69,0:12:35.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:752690,755067}Look, it's Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.31,0:12:39.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:756318,759238}Number 18.\NMy name is Meimi Haneoka.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.48,0:12:41.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:759488,761490}How old are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.74,0:12:44.86,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:761740,764868}Oh, I'm sorry. I'm 14.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.24,0:12:48.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:765244,768372}What is your idea of the perfect man?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.62,0:12:50.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:768622,770374}This I've got to hear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.05,0:13:03.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:780050,783595}Someone like my father!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.84,0:13:05.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:783846,785389}Rats.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.64,0:13:09.18,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:786640,789184}Oops, I think I goofed.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.06,0:13:16.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:792062,796442}And that concludes\Nour program for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.69,0:13:21.03,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:796692,801030}The results of today's judging\Nof these 50 contestants…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.28,0:13:23.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:801280,803782}…will be sent out within 3 days.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.03,0:13:27.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:804033,807286}There's still one left, 51!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:29.28,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:807828,809288}What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.53,0:13:31.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:809538,811290}This part of the show?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.79,0:13:35.25,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:813792,815252}What's going on here?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.50,0:13:40.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:815502,820007}– Is there someone left?\N– No, I'm sure there were only 50 girls.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.25,0:13:43.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:820257,823052}Turn on the lights!\NWhere are the lights?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.09,0:13:51.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:827097,831101}Oh, Lord, forgive me,\Nfor I use no gimmick or trick.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:52.01,0:13:53.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:832019,833604}On the screen…
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.02,0:13:56.10,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:834021,836106}St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.86,0:14:02.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:840861,842571}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.40,0:14:06.24,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:844406,846241}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:10.66,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:847785,850662}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.59,0:14:30.59,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:868597,870599}It's St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.47,0:14:35.64,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:874478,875646}Hi!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.27,0:14:42.06,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:880275,882069}What is this smoke?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.31,0:14:44.57,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:882319,884571}Is it St. Tail?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.82,0:14:47.99,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:884822,887991}Meimi, I pray God is with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.24,0:14:51.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:888242,891078}Now, drop the curtain!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.20,0:14:54.49,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:893205,894498}Seira!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.29,0:14:59.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:895290,899461}We'd better not move around now.\NBesides, you seem pretty slow.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.71,0:15:01.00,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:899711,901004}Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.67,0:15:04.46,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:901672,904466}Don't worry, you'll be safe with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.55,0:15:15.93,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:910556,915936}What's so funny?\NI haven't told any jokes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.97,0:15:19.89,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:916979,919898}Drop the curtain! Hurry!\NWhat's the holdup?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.39,0:15:24.31,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:920399,924319}Sorry, Asuka Jr.! We can't move!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.69,0:15:27.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:924695,927322}Number 51, St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.61,0:15:30.32,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:927614,930325}I am a thief! How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.03,0:15:33.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:931034,933829}Damn! You're not getting the locket!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.20,0:15:38.29,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:934204,938292}I see you, Mr. Iwasaki!\NYou won't get away!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.96,0:15:43.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:941962,943839}It's…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.71,0:15:47.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:944715,947301}…Show…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.42,0:15:50.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:948427,950804}…Time!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.77,0:16:04.19,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:959771,964193}Beauty contests are fun\Nbut how's this shampoo?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.27,0:16:08.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:965277,968071}Now, watch closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.74,0:16:13.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:971742,973535}One!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.74,0:16:15.07,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:973744,975078}Two!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.78,0:16:17.53,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:975787,977539}Three!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.88,0:16:30.05,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:987883,990052}St. Tail, that's not fair!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.14,0:16:45.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1003148,1005275}My locket.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.36,0:16:49.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1007361,1009446}I have the locket!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.24,0:16:52.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1011240,1012449}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.69,0:16:54.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1012699,1014451}Damn this smoke!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.70,0:16:57.91,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1014701,1017913}I'm definitely going\Nto get that St. Tail!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.45,0:17:06.58,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1022459,1026588}You should be ashamed.\NAs the mayor's niece, I'm embarrassed.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.83,0:17:08.38,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1026838,1028382}We're sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.42,0:17:12.80,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1029424,1032803}Rats. You're not\Ngetting away with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.05,0:17:15.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1033053,1035847}I don't care who does it,\Njust pull the rope!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.39,0:17:18.14,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1036390,1038141}Rope?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:30.11,0:17:31.78,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1050112,1051780}– Asuka Jr.!\N– Meimi!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.03,0:17:33.61,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1052030,1053615}Oh, no!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.61,0:17:36.82,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1054616,1056827}It's so heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:39.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1057327,1059830}Hurry. I've got to get out of here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.74,0:17:45.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1062749,1065377}This isn't exactly going as I planned.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.54,0:17:51.34,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1066545,1071341}– This can't be happening!\N– I've got you at last!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.76,0:17:56.13,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1073760,1076138}He'll hate me!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.35,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1078432,1080350}Let me see your face!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.60,0:18:03.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1080601,1083270}Please don't hate me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.35,0:18:06.27,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1084354,1086273}No!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.94,0:18:11.23,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1086940,1091236}Asuka Jr.! Sorry! Are you all right?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.36,0:18:19.70,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1095365,1099703}Don't arrest her!\NShe got my locket back for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.88,0:18:38.84,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1116887,1118847}Asuka Jr.?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.64,0:18:48.60,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1125646,1128607}She got my locket back for me!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.57,0:19:02.37,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1139576,1142371}It's a sure bet that I didn't pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.62,0:19:06.83,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1142621,1146833}You can never tell! Sometimes\Nthey go for things like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.50,0:19:09.75,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1147501,1149753}– Seira.\N– Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.00,0:19:12.79,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1150003,1152798}I can't wait for the results!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.04,0:19:17.30,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1153048,1157302}Don't worry about it.\NYou had the best response!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.30,0:19:24.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1162307,1164267}I goofed up.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.11,0:19:35.90,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1173110,1175904}Give it up, trying to be a star.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.44,0:19:37.44,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1176446,1177447}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.11,0:19:41.41,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1178115,1181410}Your father wouldn't approve.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.61,0:19:46.45,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1182619,1186456}If I were your father, I wouldn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.04,0:19:54.42,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1192045,1194423}Yes, you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.84,0:20:05.26,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1199845,1205267}What a disappointment!\NBoth Meimi and Rina didn't pass.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.51,0:20:10.77,saint tail default,,0,0,0,,{TIME:1205517,1210772}We thought they'd be able to\Nintroduce us to some handsome actors!
